{"content": "I need to multiply 194 \u00d7 a70 in base 11.\n\n**Step 1: Convert 194 (base 11) to base 10**\n- 194\u2081\u2081 = 1\u00d711\u00b2 + 9\u00d711\u00b9 + 4\u00d711\u2070\n- = 1\u00d7121 + 9\u00d711 + 4\u00d71\n- = 121 + 99 + 4\n- = 224\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Convert a70 (base 11) to base 10**\n- a70\u2081\u2081 = 10\u00d711\u00b2 + 7\u00d711\u00b9 + 0\u00d711\u2070\n- = 10\u00d7121 + 7\u00d711 + 0\n- = 1210 + 77 + 0\n- = 1287\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Multiply in base 10**\n- 224 \u00d7 1287 = 288,288\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 4: Convert 288,288 (base 10) to base 11**\n- 288,288 \u00f7 11 = 26,208 R 0\n- 26,208 \u00f7 11 = 2,382 R 6\n- 2,382 \u00f7 11 = 216 R 6\n- 216 \u00f7 11 = 19 R 7\n- 19 \u00f7 11 = 1 R 8\n- 1 \u00f7 11 = 0 R 1\n\nReading remainders from bottom to top: 187660\n\n187660", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 363, "completion_tokens": 396}